Subject: Open Access Report incorrect
Description: Customer is seeing incorrect data on the open access report. A share will reappear every other scan even after dropping data.
DevOps_Steps_to_Reproduce__c:
1. Run Open Access report
2. Verify shares that are not open are there

- Old report shows entire C & D drive being share
- No shares on this server

--- Remediated: 1/28

- No shares on this server any longer
- Last FSAA Exceptions 1/28 @ 1pm

Next_Steps__c: Now that we have a successful FSAA_Exceptions job for the host in question, Paul will rerun the Open Access report and let us know if the remediated share still shows.
